      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PSYCHO SUSIE (3) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (19.72) in a Grade 6 last time at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. UNMASKED (1) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 18 length eighth (20.73) at this track in a Grade 5. Can do much better this time. JEAN'S THING (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.25) at this track behind Goldstar Rodney in a P5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature again. STAINED ACES (7) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.",
